# Ignore patterns for fd, ripgrep, and other tools
# Used by:
# - fd (FZF_DEFAULT_COMMAND for fzf file search)
# - ripgrep (code search, including tmux ripgrep popup)
# - other tools that respect .ignore files
#
# This is the single source of truth for ignore patterns.
# Both .gitignore and .ignore are respected, but .ignore takes precedence.

